<i>noun</i>: 임기응변 [임기응변] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>임기응변 [임기응변]</dt><br>
<dd>extemporaneousness; impromptu; ad-hoc; temporary measure</dd><br>
<dd>그때그때의 상황에 맞게 바로 결정하거나 처리함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of making a decision on the spot, according to the situation one finds himself or herself in, on a case-by-case basis.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>